<p>What is <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Kodama Coupon</code>?</p>
<ul>
  <li>Use Kodama Coupon as a ticket for Kodama Express train.
    <ul>
      <li>You do not need to exchange the coupon for a ticket.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Only use ticket gates for JR Tokaiâ€™s SHINKANSEN train!
    <ul>
      <li>Show the Kodama Coupon at the gates.</li>
      <li>Do not use automatic gates.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Only board the train with the conditions specified on your Kodama Coupon regarding the effective date /zone / train and reserved seat.
    <ul>
      <li>You cannot board any other trains including non-reserved seats.</li>
      <li>You cannot stopover or board the train midway in a zone covered by your Kodama Coupon. If you do so, you will be required to purchase extra ticket / special express ticket from the station of departure.ï¼ˆin this
case, the Kodama Coupon is not refundable.ï¼‰</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

